title: Can I get pes cse in round 2, pessat rank 461?

comments.body: Depends on if there are any seats left. But if there are vacancies, you'll definitely get it with.
I'm scared shitless and idk what to do, really depressed rn
Some would have dropped out after kcet results to go to RV, BMS, etc. So its possible for you to get their seats.
Calm down, it's fine. I'm pretty sure you'll get a seat for your rank in the 2nd round. Keep your options open tho, you never know what PES might pull.
Mostly, yes. But depends largely on the number of available seats and what rankers show up.

>you never know what PES might pull

Love how this sentence can be applied to any situation at PES
As a current Pessant, I couldn't think of any better way to phrase it.
I got it in the first round and my pessat rank was 621 so you're fine.
